          <title>Venezuela's top court issues a $10 million fine for TikTok over allegedly deadly video challenges</title>
          <description><![CDATA[CARACAS, Venezuela (AP) — Venezuela’s Supreme Court on Monday issued a $10 million fine against TikTok for “not implementing measures” to prevent viral video challenges that have allegedly led to the deaths of three Venezuelan children recently.]]></description>
